{"tid":1974775,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"和好容易 如初難","createTime":"2020-04-16T05:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T06:58:20.000Z","uid":137303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55d7a871fc62312fd1437a8302439fbfb073b97c","tid":1974775,"uid":137303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"細個以為兩個人相愛就可以去到天長地久<br />\n<br />\n第一次分開之後，兩個人毫無交集，以為大家都放低左段往事。到重遇，兩個人都怕又重蹈覆轍，唔敢太過表露對對方既心意，結果又係搞到兩敗俱傷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係認真想復合，應該好好考慮下自己係咪真係放得低自己尊嚴臉子等等先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。雖然你地一齊過，但由你地復合個下開始就應該好好放低你地一齊過既往事，將段關係當係新既戀愛，否則你只會繼續猜忌段感情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝福我最愛的，遇見更愛你的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47060cd31980be19a3908bb59cd34de81d994de","tid":1974775,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a479d1299a242975c28379d86492052235fe614","tid":1974775,"uid":39648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28faddc7c1899a53fa07fe8ee6e5d801f39bd41d","tid":1974775,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"係架 <br />\n唉 希望之後唔好再見到佢 <br />\n我會重拾往事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a647c8137af4f69d605477c6c08a7297e407ef0b","tid":1974775,"uid":137303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a479d1299a242975c28379d86492052235fe614","tid":1974775,"uid":39648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"其實我地一開始都以為可以重新嚟過<br />\n但一直避開傾起以前嘅事 <br />\n結果又導致大家越嚟越唔信任大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}